OL,3,CMan in hospital after stabbing in
OL,4,CLeicester City Centre
OL,6,FA man has been taken to hospital after
OL,7,Fa stabbing in Leicester in the early
OL,8,Fhours of Thursday morning (16 April).
OL,10,FThe stabbing happened on Charles
OL,11,FStreet in the city centre.
OL,13,FLeicestershire Police and East
OL,14,FMidlands Ambulance Service attended
OL,15,Fthe junction with Yeoman Lane and
OL,16,Ffound a man in his 20s.
OL,18,FHe was taken to hospital with injuries
OL,19,Fthat are not believed to be life
OL,20,Fthreatening.
