OL,3,CMan in hospital after stabbing in
OL,4,CLeicester City Centre
OL,6,FA search of the area was undertaken
OL,7,Fand no arrests have been made.
OL,9,FA police cordon remains at the scene
OL,10,Fand the road is still closed.
OL,12,FSergeant Steph Burnham, from the
OL,13,FCentral Leicester Neighbourhood
OL,14,FPolicing Area (NPA) said: "It was
OL,15,Freported a group of men were seen
OL,16,Frunning off towards Lee Circle, St
OL,17,FJames Street and Hill Street.
