OL,3,CMan in hospital after stabbing in
OL,4,CLeicester City Centre
OL,6,F"I'd like to speak to anyone who was
OL,7,Fin or close to Charles Street in the
OL,8,Fearly hours of this morning. We are
OL,9,Fkeen to speak to anyone with a dashcam
OL,10,Fin their vehicle and residents or
OL,11,Fbusiness owners who have a camera on
OL,12,Fthe outside of their property.
OL,14,F"Any information or footage you're
OL,15,Fable to provide, no matter how
OL,16,Finsignificant you think it is, could
OL,17,Fhelp."
